潤創業、華潤電力、華潤置地、華潤水泥控股、華潤燃氣)<br />\n4. 中國光大集團股份公司<br />\n<br />\n其餘在港國企<br />\n5. 中國電信集團公司<br />\n6. 中國聯合網絡通信集團有限公司<br />\n7. 中國移動通信集團公司<br />\n8. 華為技術有限公司<br />\n9. 中國工商銀行股份有限公司<br />\n10. 中國建設銀行股份有限公司<br />\n11. 中國建築股份有限公司<br />\n12. 中國農業銀行股份有限公司<br />\n13. 中國平安保險（集團）股份有限公司<br />\n14. 中國人壽保險（集團）公司"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:51:02.000Z","msg":"屠曱甴兒女先有用，會直接令佢地軍心散渙"},{"pid":"401693f2284449ceea8a2cb061045995c965651d","tid":1713172,"uid":116568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:51:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50ac7337eb04700d726cfd6ca62ffd3434ea4c7","tid":1713172,"uid":64914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af346ef50414299206437fb37bbb0e1fbeb51b1d","tid":1713172,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee942fc3bc5c9fa8a938551bf9b41f8565605526","tid":1713172,"uid":131481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6d4133fb361e4d4c27613036b6b829eabaa6369","tid":1713172,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:56:06.000Z","msg":"證明而家警力不足<br />\n但港島除左老銅好似冇咩動靜?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:07:22.000Z","msg":"你當香港仔係咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:08:54.000Z","msg":"d焦點去晒暴大同mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:54:10.000Z","msg":"靜靜地贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73451b1b9d4d6f25f970b1243b3c6bb96dd14089","tid":1713172,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c50ac7337eb04700d726cfd6ca62ffd3434ea4c7","tid":1713172,"uid":64914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af346ef504142992